    "en": {
      "title": "Covid rears its head again",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "62 people infected with Covid and three infected deaths were reported yesterday (19).",
        "According to the health department, the increase in the number of Covid-infected people happened after about two and a half months.",
        "Dr. Samitha Ginige, Head of the Epidemiology Department, said that a problematic situation may arise in the future due to the rise in the number of people infected with Covid."
      ],
